    <h3><u>THE CHURCH OF PENTECOST </u></h3>
    <p>
        THE CHURCH OF PENTECOST WAS FOUNDED BY AN IRISH MISSIONARY SENT BY THE 
        APOSTOLIC CHURCH IN THE UNITED KINGDOM TO GOLD COAST IN 1937, PASTOR JAMES MCKEOWN
